    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/16/125391187/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_5644497541969783922.png",
                "id": "talent61308",
                "key": "碎濤旋躍",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "碎濤旋躍"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素傷害</span>，此角色每有3點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">無盡食慾</span>提供的額外最大生命，此傷害+1（最多+4）。然後<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">捨棄</span>1張原本元素骰費用最高的手牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/16/125391187/923db325e73849fb31b138dfdd1a0cab_7733758795737032951.png",
                "id": "talent76682",
                "key": "迸落星雨",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "迸落星雨"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素傷害</span>，對敵方所有後臺角色造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span>。召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">黑色幻影</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/16/125391187/dec2f5cea15b6652638355fb66ef2d98_3322596701824774613.png",
                "id": "talent92129",
                "key": "橫噬鯨吞",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "橫噬鯨吞"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">被動技能</span></p><p>【被動】戰鬥開始時，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">深噬之域</span>。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">深噬之域</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">捨棄</span>或<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">調和</span>的卡牌，會被吞噬。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">每吞噬3張牌：</span>吞星之鯨獲得1點額外最大生命；如果其中存在原本元素骰費用值相同的牌，則額外獲得1點；如果3張均相同，再額外獲得1點。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/16/125391187/edd2da5186218246a20f5b0d52d2c634_9035287703213048930.png",
                "id": "talent34732",
                "key": "無盡食慾",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "無盡食慾"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">入場時：</span>獲得我方已吞噬卡牌中最高元素骰費用值的「攻擊力」，獲得該費用的已吞噬卡牌數量的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段和我方宣布結束時：</span>造成此牌「攻擊力」值的<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方出戰角色受到傷害時：</span>抵消1點傷害，然後此牌<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數-</span>2。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/16/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_4062036510596935197.png",
                "id": "talent88977",
                "key": "黑色幻影",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/16/125391187/bc781100ebefe81947d3fac533aaed65_5115254692696251703.png",
                "title": "黑色幻影"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸發</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">凍結</span>：本傷害+1，使目標本回合無法行動（受到<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>傷害後提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綻放</span>：本傷害+1，生成使下次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>傷害+2的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「草原核」</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/16/125391187/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_843743938728384976.png",
                "id": "talent43017",
                "key": "水元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著雷元素，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點穿透傷害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點穿透傷害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本傷害+1，生成使下2次草元素或雷元素傷害+1的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[激化領域]</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/16/125391187/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_2624669856489141289.png",
                "id": "talent10784",
                "key": "雷元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">捨棄</span></p><p>透過行動牌或角色技能的效果，將行動牌從手牌或牌庫中棄置。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>穿透傷害無法受到傷害加成，但是也無法被護盾、傷害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">調和</span></p><p>為了進行元素調和，而將行動牌從手牌中棄置。</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/16/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_9218828874962305021.png",
